<h3 id="反射的性能问题与优化">反射的性能问题与优化</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">反射调用慢的原因：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 安全检查：每次调用都进行访问权限检查
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   → 优化：setAccessible(true) + 缓存
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 参数包装/解包：基本类型需装箱拆箱
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   → 优化：使用特定类型方法（setInt, invokeExact）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 方法分派：无法内联优化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   → 优化：JIT编译后可能优化，但不稳定
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 元数据查找：每次查找Method/Field对象
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   → 优化：缓存Method/Field对象</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 反射优化：缓存Method对象</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">ReflectiveCache</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">private</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">final</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Method</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">CACHED_METHOD</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">static</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="n">Method</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">m</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">User</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">getDeclaredMethod</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;setName&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="n">m</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setAccessible</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 关闭安全检查</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="n">CACHED_METHOD</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">m</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">catch</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Exception</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="k">throw</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">RuntimeException</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">setName</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">User</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">user</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kd">throws</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Exception</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">CACHED_METHOD</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">invoke</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">user</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 复用缓存的Method</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="methodhandle更高效的反射替代">MethodHandle：更高效的反射替代</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// MethodHandle使用</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">MethodHandles</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">Lookup</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">lookup</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">MethodHandles</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">lookup</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">MethodType</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">mt</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">MethodType</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">methodType</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">MethodHandle</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">mh</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">lookup</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">findVirtual</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">User</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;setName&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">mt</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">User</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">user</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">User</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">mh</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">invoke</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">user</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;Tom&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 直接调用，无反射开销</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// invokeExact要求参数类型精确匹配</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">mh</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">invokeExact</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">user</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;Tom&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">编译期检查类型</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>反射 vs MethodHandle vs LambdaMetafactory</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>JUC并发工具包</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/juc%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/juc%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%85/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="juc并发工具包">JUC并发工具包</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：JUC通过Lock体系替代synchronized提供灵活锁机制，通过Semaphore控制并发数，通过CountDownLatch和CyclicBarrier协调多线程执行节奏，通过CompletableFuture实现异步编排，覆盖了从互斥到协作的完整并发控制场景。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="juc通过显式锁信号量栅栏异步future四类工具提供了比synchronized更精细的并发控制能力">JUC通过显式锁、信号量、栅栏、异步Future四类工具，提供了比synchronized更精细的并发控制能力</h2>
<h3 id="lock体系比synchronized更灵活的锁机制">Lock体系：比synchronized更灵活的锁机制</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>ReentrantLock</th>
          <th>synchronized</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>可中断</td>
          <td>支持lockInterruptibly()</td>
          <td>不支持</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>可超时</td>
          <td>支持tryLock(timeout)</td>
          <td>不支持</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>公平性</td>
          <td>支持公平/非公平模式</td>
          <td>非公平</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>条件变量</td>
          <td>多个Condition</td>
          <td>一个wait/notify</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>尝试获取</td>
          <td>tryLock()</td>
          <td>无</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>性能</td>
          <td>JDK6+优化后接近</td>
          <td>同左</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// ReentrantLock基本用法</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">ReentrantLock</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">ReentrantLock</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">lock</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 获取锁</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="c1">// 临界区</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">finally</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">unlock</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 必须在finally中释放</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 可中断锁</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">lockInterruptibly</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="c1">// 可被Thread.interrupt()中断</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">finally</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">unlock</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 尝试获取锁（不阻塞）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">tryLock</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">TimeUnit</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">SECONDS</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="c1">// 获取到锁</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">finally</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="n">lock</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">unlock</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">else</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="c1">// 超时未获取到锁</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>ReadWriteLock：读写分离提升并发</strong></p>]]></description></item><item><title>事务机制</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/%E4%BA%8B%E5%8A%A1/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="事务机制">事务机制</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：事务通过ACID特性保证数据一致性，隔离级别在一致性和并发性能之间权衡，Spring通过声明式事务简化编程，分布式事务通过2PC、TCC、Saga等模式解决跨服务一致性。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="事务通过acid保证数据一致性隔离级别控制并发副作用分布式事务通过补偿机制实现最终一致性">事务通过ACID保证数据一致性，隔离级别控制并发副作用，分布式事务通过补偿机制实现最终一致性</h2>
<h3 id="acid与隔离级别一致性与并发的权衡">ACID与隔离级别：一致性与并发的权衡</h3>
<p><strong>ACID特性</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>实现机制</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Atomicity（原子性）</td>
          <td>要么全成功，要么全回滚</td>
          <td>Undo Log</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Consistency（一致性）</td>
          <td>数据状态合法</td>
          <td>约束+触发器+应用逻辑</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Isolation（隔离性）</td>
          <td>事务间互不干扰</td>
          <td>MVCC + 锁</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Durability（持久性）</td>
          <td>提交后数据不丢失</td>
          <td>Redo Log + 磁盘写入</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>隔离级别与并发问题</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>隔离级别</th>
          <th>脏读</th>
          <th>不可重复读</th>
          <th>幻读</th>
          <th>实现</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>READ UNCOMMITTED</td>
          <td>✗允许</td>
          <td>✗允许</td>
          <td>✗允许</td>
          <td>无锁</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>READ COMMITTED</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>✗允许</td>
          <td>✗允许</td>
          <td>MVCC</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>REPEATABLE READ</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>✗允许（MySQL Innodb禁止）</td>
          <td>MVCC + 间隙锁</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SERIALIZABLE</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>✓禁止</td>
          <td>所有操作加锁</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">并发问题示例：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">脏读（Dirty Read）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  事务A读取 → 事务B修改但未提交 → 事务A读取到未提交数据 → 事务B回滚
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">不可重复读（Non-repeatable Read）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  事务A读取 → 事务B修改并提交 → 事务A再次读取，数据变化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">幻读（Phantom Read）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  事务A查询（返回3条）→ 事务B插入新数据并提交 → 事务A再次查询，返回4条</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="spring声明式事务transactional">Spring声明式事务：@Transactional</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@Transactional</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">propagation</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Propagation</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">REQUIRED</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">   </span><span class="c1">// 传播行为</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">isolation</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Isolation</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">READ_COMMITTED</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="c1">// 隔离级别</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">timeout</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">30</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">                          </span><span class="c1">// 超时时间（秒）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">readOnly</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">                      </span><span class="c1">// 是否只读</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">rollbackFor</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Exception</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="w">          </span><span class="c1">// 哪些异常触发回滚</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kt">void</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">transfer</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">fromId</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">toId</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">BigDecimal</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">amount</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">accountDao</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">decrease</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">fromId</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">amount</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">accountDao</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">increase</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">toId</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">amount</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>传播行为</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>线程池原理与调优</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E6%B1%A0/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E6%B1%A0/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="线程池原理与调优">线程池原理与调优</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：线程池通过复用线程减少创建销毁开销，通过阻塞队列缓冲任务，通过拒绝策略处理超负荷，核心参数（核心线程数、最大线程数、队列容量）的配置直接决定了系统的吞吐和稳定性。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="线程池通过复用线程和队列缓冲实现资源控制核心参数配置不当是导致生产故障的主要原因">线程池通过复用线程和队列缓冲实现资源控制，核心参数配置不当是导致生产故障的主要原因</h2>
<h3 id="threadpoolexecutor核心参数">ThreadPoolExecutor核心参数</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">ThreadPoolExecutor</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">corePoolSize</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">           </span><span class="c1">// 核心线程数</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">maximumPoolSize</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">        </span><span class="c1">// 最大线程数</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">keepAliveTime</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">         </span><span class="c1">// 空闲线程存活时间</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">TimeUnit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">unit</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">              </span><span class="c1">// 时间单位</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">BlockingQueue</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">Runnable</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">workQueue</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 任务队列</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">ThreadFactory</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">threadFactory</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">         </span><span class="c1">// 线程工厂</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">RejectedExecutionHandler</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">handler</span><span class="w">     </span><span class="c1">// 拒绝策略</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>参数作用与任务提交流程</strong>：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">提交任务 → 当前线程数 &lt; corePoolSize？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    → 是：创建新线程执行任务
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    → 否：队列未满？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        → 是：任务入队列
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        → 否：当前线程数 &lt; maximumPoolSize？
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            → 是：创建新线程（临时线程）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            → 否：执行拒绝策略
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">线程空闲超过keepAliveTime：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    - 当前线程数 &gt; corePoolSize：销毁多余线程
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    - 当前线程数 &lt;= corePoolSize：保留（除非allowCoreThreadTimeOut=true）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>JDK提供的快捷创建方法</strong>：</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>